results.lead_paragraph: CAPE KENNEDY, Fla.-- For many months, the Air Force and the National Aeronautics and Space Administration have operated separate weekend automobile tours of the space installations here. Now these have been consolidated into one tour that takes in both the Cape Kennedy Air Force Station and the Kennedy Spaceport. The tour covers 50 miles and lasts about two and one-half hours.
